{
  "id": "setup_logging_framework@1",
  "version": "1.0",
  "env_id": "intellij_idea_env@0.1",
  "description": "Migrate the 'library-app' project from using System.out.println to SLF4J with Logback. Add 'slf4j-api' (v2.0.9) and 'logback-classic' (v1.4.14) to the project dependencies. Configure Logback with a console appender and DEBUG level in src/main/resources/logback.xml. Replace all System.out and System.err print statements in the Java source files with appropriate SLF4J logger calls and ensure the project compiles successfully.",
